  "Description": {
    "English": "Shatter-proof, scratch-resistant glass with a self-cleaning, UV-cured coating, for general construction use.<br><br>Refined from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Silicate</span> powder. Extract silicate from the earth with a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Terrain Manipulator</span>.<br><br>Can be crafted from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Frost Crystals</span> extracted from plants on <span class=\"name name-technology\">frozen</span> worlds.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "耐震且耐划的玻璃，具有自动清洗功能，采用紫外线光固化涂料，用于一般建造。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-stellar\">硅酸盐</span>粉末精炼而成。用<span class=\"name name-technology\">地形操纵器</span>从土地上提取硅酸盐。<br><br>可用提取自<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻星球</span>上植物的<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜水晶</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "耐震且耐划的玻璃，具有自动清洗功能，采用紫外线光固化涂料，用于一般建造。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-stellar\">硅酸盐</span>粉末精炼而成。用<span class=\"name name-technology\">地形操纵器</span>从土地上提取硅酸盐。<br><br>可用提取自<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻星球</span>上植物的<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜水晶</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "防刮安全玻璃，表面塗層能自動清潔、經紫外線固化，可用於一般建築工程。<br><br>利用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">矽酸</span>粉精製而成。矽酸則是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">地形改造器</span>自泥土萃取。<br><br>可使用自<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰雪</span>世界植物萃取出的<span class=\"name name-technology\">霜晶</span>製作。"
  },
