  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Refine from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Silicate Powder</span>. Extract silicate from the earth with a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Terrain Manipulator</span>.<br>Craft with <span class=\"name name-technology\">Frost Crystals</span> harvested from <span class=\"name name-technology\">frozen worlds</span>.  Learn the blueprint with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Construction Overseer</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">硅酸盐粉末</span>精炼而成。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">地形操纵器</span>从土地提取硅酸盐。<br>用采自<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻世界</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜水晶</span>制作。在<span class=\"name name-technology\">建造监督者</span>的协助下学会设计图。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">硅酸盐粉末</span>精炼而成。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">地形操纵器</span>从土地提取硅酸盐。<br>用采自<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻世界</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰霜水晶</span>制作。在<span class=\"name name-technology\">建造监督者</span>的协助下学会设计图。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-stellar\">矽酸粉</span>精製。矽酸可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">地形改造器</span>從土中萃取。<br>利用從<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰雪世界</span>採集的<span class=\"name name-technology\">霜晶</span>製作。借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">建築監督者</span>之力學習設計圖。"
